She has long, straight brown hair fanned out on the bed, and she's looking directly at the camera with a neutral expression. Her arms are stretched above her head, creating leading lines that draw attention to her face. She's wearing a white, ribbed, crop-top tank that reveals her midriff, and dark blue jeans that are slightly unbuttoned, showing a hint of her white underwear. Her skin is fair, and she has a slim, petite build. The lighting is soft and even, highlighting her features and the texture of the bed sheets. The composition follows the rule of thirds, with her face and arms positioned in the upper third and her torso and jeans in the lower third. The overall style is casual and relaxed. ;
